    public class DefaultAssociativeLinkageSystem6
extends DefaultAssociativeLinkageSystem4
    version six of the linkage system. Links are still created in the same manner (as 4), however since there is no learning of the strengths, the procedural listener is no longer needed, so we override and return null.
